  ('16-18m','16–18 months',16,18,true,'ent_cluster_16_18_safer_home','Keep a faster toddler safer',8,true,'ent_need_16_18_safer_exploring','Keep a faster toddler safer','Your toddler may be taller, quicker and more determined than your last safety sweep allowed for. This cluster focuses on fresh checks, not panic buying: stairs, cupboards, furniture, blind cords, button batteries and bath or water moments that need a second look now.','for_you','cat_stair_gates','Stair gate fit check','Stair Gates',1,'If your toddler is walking, squatting or trying steps, stair safety needs a fresh look. The useful task is not just owning a gate. It is checking placement, fit, closing habits and whether the route has changed.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',1,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,'If gates are already installed, check they still close and latch properly.',NULL,'conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('16-18m','16–18 months',16,18,true,'ent_cluster_16_18_safer_home','Keep a faster toddler safer',8,true,'ent_need_16_18_safer_exploring','Keep a faster toddler safer','Your toddler may be taller, quicker and more determined than your last safety sweep allowed for. This cluster focuses on fresh checks, not panic buying: stairs, cupboards, furniture, blind cords, button batteries and bath or water moments that need a second look now.','for_you','cat_cupboard_locks','Cupboard locks and safer storage','Cupboard Locks',2,'A toddler who can walk, squat and copy you may reach places that were irrelevant a few months ago. Recheck medicines, cleaning products, sharp objects and breakables, then decide whether locks or higher storage are needed.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',2,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,'This is a safety check first; buy only if storage cannot be made safer another way.',NULL,'conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('16-18m','16–18 months',16,18,true,'ent_cluster_16_18_safer_home','Keep a faster toddler safer',8,true,'ent_need_16_18_safer_exploring','Keep a faster toddler safer','Your toddler may be taller, quicker and more determined than your last safety sweep allowed for. This cluster focuses on fresh checks, not panic buying: stairs, cupboards, furniture, blind cords, button batteries and bath or water moments that need a second look now.','for_you','cat_furniture_window_checks','Furniture, window and cord checks','Furniture Window Checks',3,'A faster, taller toddler can climb, pull and reach in new ways. Recheck bookcases, dressers, TV stands, windows, low furniture near windows and trailing cords, especially in bedrooms and rooms where they play alone for a moment.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',3,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,'This is a fresh sweep, not a shopping prompt.',NULL,'conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('16-18m','16–18 months',16,18,true,'ent_cluster_16_18_safer_home','Keep a faster toddler safer',8,true,'ent_need_16_18_safer_exploring','Keep a faster toddler safer','Your toddler may be taller, quicker and more determined than your last safety sweep allowed for. This cluster focuses on fresh checks, not panic buying: stairs, cupboards, furniture, blind cords, button batteries and bath or water moments that need a second look now.','for_you','cat_button_battery_check','Button battery checks','Button Battery Check',4,'Remote controls, light-up toys, cards, scales and thermometers can hide button batteries. As curiosity and reach grow, check compartments are secure and keep loose batteries out of reach.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',4,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,'A five-minute sweep is more valuable than buying more safety kit.',NULL,'conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('16-18m','16–18 months',16,18,true,'ent_cluster_16_18_safer_home','Keep a faster toddler safer',8,true,'ent_need_16_18_safer_exploring','Keep a faster toddler safer','Your toddler may be taller, quicker and more determined than your last safety sweep allowed for. This cluster focuses on fresh checks, not panic buying: stairs, cupboards, furniture, blind cords, button batteries and bath or water moments that need a second look now.','for_you','cat_bath_water_supervision','Bath and water supervision','Bath Water Supervision',5,'Water play can be brilliant for pouring, pretend washing and sensory play, but the safety rule stays simple: stay close and supervise. Treat baths, paddling pools, buckets and water tables as adult-present activities.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',5,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,'Use cups and bowls you already own; supervision matters more than kit.',NULL,'conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_pretend_worlds','Pretend play gets richer',1,true,'ent_need_22_24_pretend_worlds','I’m making little worlds','Your toddler may be moving from copying one action to building tiny scenes: feeding a teddy, pouring pretend tea, putting animals in a bus or giving a doll a check-up. Simple props help them practise language, care and imagination through the routines they already know.','for_your_child','cat_play_kitchen_household_props','Play kitchen and household props','Play Kitchen Household Props',1,'A spoon, pan, phone or tiny basket can help your toddler copy the everyday life they are watching. Around this stage, those copied actions may start joining together into small pretend scenes, giving them a playful way to practise words, care and sequencing.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','A strong second-birthday gift if the family has space.','Check whether they already have a kitchen or plenty of pretend food.','Play kitchen and household props','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_pretend_worlds','Pretend play gets richer',1,true,'ent_need_22_24_pretend_worlds','I’m making little worlds','Your toddler may be moving from copying one action to building tiny scenes: feeding a teddy, pouring pretend tea, putting animals in a bus or giving a doll a check-up. Simple props help them practise language, care and imagination through the routines they already know.','for_your_child','cat_doll_soft_toy_care','Soft doll or cuddly care play','Doll Soft Toy Care',2,'Feeding, cuddling, wiping or putting a doll to bed can be a simple way for your toddler to copy real care routines. It supports pretend play, early empathy and the kind of language that comes from acting out what they see at home.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',2,true,true,true,'Good gift','A warm gift when the child is starting to care for teddies or dolls.','A soft toy they already love can work too.','Soft doll or cuddly care play','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_pretend_worlds','Pretend play gets richer',1,true,'ent_need_22_24_pretend_worlds','I’m making little worlds','Your toddler may be moving from copying one action to building tiny scenes: feeding a teddy, pouring pretend tea, putting animals in a bus or giving a doll a check-up. Simple props help them practise language, care and imagination through the routines they already know.','for_your_child','cat_child_cleaning_helper_set','Little cleaning and helper sets','Child Cleaning Helper Set',3,'A small broom, cloth or pretend spray bottle can meet the ‘I help’ urge without turning the real job into chaos. It gives your toddler a role to copy, language to hear and a repeatable routine they can feel proud of.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',3,true,true,true,'Good gift','A thoughtful gift for a child who copies chores.','Real cloths and a safe brush may be enough before buying a full set.','Little cleaning and helper sets','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
