  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_words_together','Words are joining up',2,true,'ent_need_22_24_words_together','I’m putting words together','Around two, words, gestures and looks can start working together. Your toddler may point at pictures, copy phrases, make small choices or try two-word ideas. Books, naming walks and pretend conversations give those new words somewhere useful to go.','for_your_child','cat_picture_story_books','Picture books with a little story','Picture Story Books',1,'Books with clear pictures and simple story beats give your toddler a reason to point, name, guess and copy phrases. Around two, shared reading can shift from naming one object to talking about what is happening next.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','A safe, classic second-birthday gift.','Books are low-risk, but choose one that adds a new theme.','Picture books with a little story','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
