  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_move_purpose','Running, kicking and climbing',4,true,'ent_need_22_24_move_purpose','I’m moving with purpose','Movement may look more intentional now: running across the park, kicking a ball, climbing low steps or carrying something important from one room to another. The best ideas give your toddler a safe reason to move, not just a bigger thing to buy.','for_your_child','cat_large_balls','Large balls for kicking and chasing','Large Balls',1,'A large soft ball can turn big energy into a clear game: kick, chase, stop, try again. Around two, this supports balance, coordination and early turn-taking without needing organised sport.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','A safe, active second-birthday gift.','Choose a size they can kick, not a hard adult ball.','Large balls for kicking and chasing','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_move_purpose','Running, kicking and climbing',4,true,'ent_need_22_24_move_purpose','I’m moving with purpose','Movement may look more intentional now: running across the park, kicking a ball, climbing low steps or carrying something important from one room to another. The best ideas give your toddler a safe reason to move, not just a bigger thing to buy.','for_your_child','cat_balance_bike_scooter','First balance bike or scooter goes','Balance Bike Scooter',2,'A balance bike or beginner scooter can be brilliant for some two-year-olds, but fit matters more than age. The right option is light, low and easy to stop when your toddler inevitably gets off and asks you to carry it.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',2,true,true,true,'Good gift','A bigger gift, best checked with the parents first.','Ask the parents before buying; size, storage and confidence matter.','First balance bike or scooter goes','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_move_purpose','Running, kicking and climbing',4,true,'ent_need_22_24_move_purpose','I’m moving with purpose','Movement may look more intentional now: running across the park, kicking a ball, climbing low steps or carrying something important from one room to another. The best ideas give your toddler a safe reason to move, not just a bigger thing to buy.','for_your_child','cat_tricycle_scooter','Ride-ons and beginner scooters','Tricycle Scooter',3,'Some toddlers want the thrill of wheels before they are ready for a balance bike. Stable ride-ons and beginner scooters can offer movement practice if they fit the child, the space and the adult''s willingness to carry it home.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',3,true,true,true,'Good gift','A parent-approved gift when outdoor space and storage fit.','Best agreed with parents first.','Ride-ons and beginner scooters','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_move_purpose','Running, kicking and climbing',4,true,'ent_need_22_24_move_purpose','I’m moving with purpose','Movement may look more intentional now: running across the park, kicking a ball, climbing low steps or carrying something important from one room to another. The best ideas give your toddler a safe reason to move, not just a bigger thing to buy.','for_your_child','cat_park_climbing_play','Park climbs and low obstacles','Park Climbing Play',4,'Climbing is often less about thrill-seeking and more about testing what the body can do. Low steps, playground edges and small slopes give your toddler a reason to practise balance and planning while you stay close.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',4,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,'Park climbs and low obstacles','conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_move_purpose','Running, kicking and climbing',4,true,'ent_need_22_24_move_purpose','I’m moving with purpose','Movement may look more intentional now: running across the park, kicking a ball, climbing low steps or carrying something important from one room to another. The best ideas give your toddler a safe reason to move, not just a bigger thing to buy.','for_your_child','cat_jump_hoops_beanbags','Jump hoops and beanbags','Jump Hoops Beanbags',5,'A hoop on the floor, soft beanbag or pretend stepping stone can create a tiny movement challenge at home: step in, step out, throw, fetch, repeat. It is a useful option for rainy days or pre-dinner energy.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',5,true,true,true,'Good gift','A compact active-play gift for indoor or garden games.',NULL,'Jump hoops and beanbags','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_move_purpose','Running, kicking and climbing',4,true,'ent_need_22_24_move_purpose','I’m moving with purpose','Movement may look more intentional now: running across the park, kicking a ball, climbing low steps or carrying something important from one room to another. The best ideas give your toddler a safe reason to move, not just a bigger thing to buy.','for_your_child','cat_balance_stepping_stones','Balance paths and stepping stones','Balance Stepping Stones',6,'Stepping from cushion to mat to low stone can become a little adventure. It supports balance, coordination and planning, especially when your toddler has a job: rescue the teddy, deliver the parcel, reach the island.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',6,true,true,true,'Good gift','A more unusual movement gift, best where there is floor space.','Cushions and mats can do the job before buying stepping stones.','Balance paths and stepping stones','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_move_purpose','Running, kicking and climbing',4,true,'ent_need_22_24_move_purpose','I’m moving with purpose','Movement may look more intentional now: running across the park, kicking a ball, climbing low steps or carrying something important from one room to another. The best ideas give your toddler a safe reason to move, not just a bigger thing to buy.','for_your_child','cat_walk_with_job','A walk with a job','Walk With Job',7,'Giving your toddler a small mission can change a walk from aimless to exciting: carry the letter, spot red doors, find three sticks, push the buggy for ten steps. It turns movement into independence and language too.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',7,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,'A walk with a job','conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
