  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_body_routines','Meals, potty and body signals',6,true,'ent_need_22_24_body_routines','I’m noticing body routines','Meals, nappies and bathroom routines can become more noticeable now. Some toddlers are curious about the potty; others are not. This is a good stage to make body routines familiar, keep mealtimes safe and offer practice without making independence feel like a test.','for_both','cat_potty_chair','Potty chair for practice sitting','Potty Chair',1,'Some 22–24 month-olds are curious about the potty; some are nowhere near ready. A potty can be useful if it is framed as gentle practice and familiarity, not a deadline to be dry.','for_both','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,false,false,'Parent buy',NULL,'Only worth buying when you are ready to make it part of the routine.','Potty chair for practice sitting','conor','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_body_routines','Meals, potty and body signals',6,true,'ent_need_22_24_body_routines','I’m noticing body routines','Meals, nappies and bathroom routines can become more noticeable now. Some toddlers are curious about the potty; others are not. This is a good stage to make body routines familiar, keep mealtimes safe and offer practice without making independence feel like a test.','for_both','cat_toilet_training_seat_step','Toilet seat and foot support','Toilet Training Seat Step',2,'For toddlers who prefer the big toilet, a child seat and foot support can help them feel secure. It is a practical setup choice, not a must-have, and should follow the child''s readiness rather than age alone.','for_both','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',2,true,false,false,'Parent buy',NULL,NULL,'Toilet seat and foot support','conor','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_body_routines','Meals, potty and body signals',6,true,'ent_need_22_24_body_routines','I’m noticing body routines','Meals, nappies and bathroom routines can become more noticeable now. Some toddlers are curious about the potty; others are not. This is a good stage to make body routines familiar, keep mealtimes safe and offer practice without making independence feel like a test.','for_both','cat_potty_story_books','Potty and bathroom books','Potty Story Books',3,'A simple potty story can make bathroom routines less strange before formal training starts. It lets your toddler hear the words, see the steps and copy the idea with a teddy or doll when they are interested.','for_both','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',3,true,true,true,'Good gift','A useful small gift only if the parents are ready for potty talk.','Ask first; not every family wants potty gifts.','Potty and bathroom books','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_body_routines','Meals, potty and body signals',6,true,'ent_need_22_24_body_routines','I’m noticing body routines','Meals, nappies and bathroom routines can become more noticeable now. Some toddlers are curious about the potty; others are not. This is a good stage to make body routines familiar, keep mealtimes safe and offer practice without making independence feel like a test.','for_both','cat_training_pants','Training pants and easy-off clothes','Training Pants',4,'Training pants and easy-off clothes are only useful when a family is actively practising. They can reduce friction once the child is ready, but buying them too early can create clutter and pressure.','for_both','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',4,true,false,false,'Parent buy',NULL,'Hold off until the family is genuinely starting.','Training pants and easy-off clothes','conor','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_body_routines','Meals, potty and body signals',6,true,'ent_need_22_24_body_routines','I’m noticing body routines','Meals, nappies and bathroom routines can become more noticeable now. Some toddlers are curious about the potty; others are not. This is a good stage to make body routines familiar, keep mealtimes safe and offer practice without making independence feel like a test.','for_both','cat_toddler_cutlery','Toddler spoons and small forks','Toddler Cutlery',5,'Eating with a spoon is a useful two-year signal, but it will still be messy. A small spoon or fork can help your toddler practise hand control and independence while adults keep food safe and portions manageable.','for_both','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',5,true,true,true,'Good gift','A practical add-on gift, not the main present.','Many families already have toddler cutlery.','Toddler spoons and small forks','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_body_routines','Meals, potty and body signals',6,true,'ent_need_22_24_body_routines','I’m noticing body routines','Meals, nappies and bathroom routines can become more noticeable now. Some toddlers are curious about the potty; others are not. This is a good stage to make body routines familiar, keep mealtimes safe and offer practice without making independence feel like a test.','for_both','cat_open_cup','Open-cup and pouring practice','Open Cup',6,'A small open cup, a little jug or bath-time pouring can give your toddler safe practice with control, spilling and trying again. Keep it low stakes: a splash in the bath is often the best teacher.','for_both','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',6,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,'Use bath cups or a small plastic cup first.','Open-cup and pouring practice','conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
