  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_feelings_play','Feelings, choices and turn-taking',7,true,'ent_need_22_24_feelings_play','I’m learning it’s not all mine','At this age, toddlers can be deeply sociable and fiercely possessive within the same five minutes. Books, ball turns, little choices and care play can help them practise waiting, naming feelings and noticing other people, without expecting polished sharing yet.','for_your_child','cat_feelings_faces_books','Feeling stories and face books','Feelings Faces Books',1,'A book with clear faces can help your toddler notice happy, sad, cross or tired without needing a lecture. Naming feelings during calm moments can make the hard moments slightly easier to talk about later.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','A gentle second-birthday gift with long usefulness.',NULL,'Feeling stories and face books','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_feelings_play','Feelings, choices and turn-taking',7,true,'ent_need_22_24_feelings_play','I’m learning it’s not all mine','At this age, toddlers can be deeply sociable and fiercely possessive within the same five minutes. Books, ball turns, little choices and care play can help them practise waiting, naming feelings and noticing other people, without expecting polished sharing yet.','for_your_child','cat_teddy_care_play','Teddy care and repair play','Teddy Care Play',2,'Putting a blanket on teddy, giving a pretend drink or checking a sore paw can help toddlers act out care before they can fully explain it. It is a simple way to practise noticing and responding to others.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',2,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,'A favourite teddy is enough.','Teddy care and repair play','conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_feelings_play','Feelings, choices and turn-taking',7,true,'ent_need_22_24_feelings_play','I’m learning it’s not all mine','At this age, toddlers can be deeply sociable and fiercely possessive within the same five minutes. Books, ball turns, little choices and care play can help them practise waiting, naming feelings and noticing other people, without expecting polished sharing yet.','for_your_child','cat_first_turn_taking_games','Tiny turn-taking games','First Turn Taking Games',3,'Taking turns does not need a board game yet. It can be one roll each, one block each, one puppet hello each. The shorter and more visible the turn, the easier it is for your toddler to understand.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',3,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,'Tiny turn-taking games','conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_feelings_play','Feelings, choices and turn-taking',7,true,'ent_need_22_24_feelings_play','I’m learning it’s not all mine','At this age, toddlers can be deeply sociable and fiercely possessive within the same five minutes. Books, ball turns, little choices and care play can help them practise waiting, naming feelings and noticing other people, without expecting polished sharing yet.','for_your_child','cat_roll_ball_turns','Roll-the-ball turns','Roll Ball Turns',4,'Rolling a ball back and forth gives turn-taking a clear rhythm: my go, your go, again. It supports social play, movement and waiting without expecting a two-year-old to share their favourite toy perfectly.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',4,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,'Roll-the-ball turns','conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_feelings_play','Feelings, choices and turn-taking',7,true,'ent_need_22_24_feelings_play','I’m learning it’s not all mine','At this age, toddlers can be deeply sociable and fiercely possessive within the same five minutes. Books, ball turns, little choices and care play can help them practise waiting, naming feelings and noticing other people, without expecting polished sharing yet.','for_your_child','cat_peer_play_books','Books about other children','Peer Play Books',5,'Stories about toddlers playing, grabbing, waiting or helping can give names to real situations. They are useful before playdates, nursery days or any stage where ‘mine’ is getting louder.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',5,true,true,true,'Good gift','A thoughtful gift for a nursery starter or sociable toddler.',NULL,'Books about other children','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_feelings_play','Feelings, choices and turn-taking',7,true,'ent_need_22_24_feelings_play','I’m learning it’s not all mine','At this age, toddlers can be deeply sociable and fiercely possessive within the same five minutes. Books, ball turns, little choices and care play can help them practise waiting, naming feelings and noticing other people, without expecting polished sharing yet.','for_your_child','cat_calm_corner_tools','Quiet basket for big feelings','Calm Corner Tools',6,'A few calm items in one place can help adults offer a reset without making feelings wrong. Think a soft book, cuddly toy, sensory bottle or familiar blanket, used with you nearby rather than as a punishment corner.','for_your_child','setup','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',6,false,false,false,'Setup',NULL,'Use familiar comfort items before buying anything new.','Quiet basket for big feelings','conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_feelings_play','Feelings, choices and turn-taking',7,true,'ent_need_22_24_feelings_play','I’m learning it’s not all mine','At this age, toddlers can be deeply sociable and fiercely possessive within the same five minutes. Books, ball turns, little choices and care play can help them practise waiting, naming feelings and noticing other people, without expecting polished sharing yet.','for_your_child','cat_tiny_choice_moments','Tiny choice moments','Tiny Choice Moments',7,'Two small choices can help a toddler feel heard: red cup or blue cup, boots or trainers, this book or that one. It is useful because it protects the adult''s boundary while giving the child a real say.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',7,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,'Tiny choice moments','conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_furniture_window_checks','Furniture, stair and window checks','Furniture Window Checks',1,'As toddlers climb and reach higher, familiar rooms can change risk. Recheck climbable furniture, window access, stair gates and anything that has quietly become a stepping stone.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',1,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Furniture, stair and window checks','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_stair_gates','Stair gate and doorway review','Stair Gates',2,'A stair gate that worked last month may need checking once your toddler is taller, faster or trying to climb it. Look for secure fitting, correct use and whether the gate still fits the way your household moves.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',2,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Stair gate and doorway review','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_cupboard_locks','Cupboard locks and safer storage','Cupboard Locks',3,'A two-year-old can suddenly open, climb, pull and investigate in new ways. Recheck medicines, cleaning products, sharp tools and heavy pans, especially in cupboards that used to feel safely out of reach.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',3,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Cupboard locks and safer storage','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_button_battery_check','Button battery and magnet check','Button Battery Check',4,'Toys, remotes, cards, candles and novelty items can hide button batteries or small magnets. A quick sweep matters more now because your toddler can open more things and still may explore with their mouth.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',4,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Button battery and magnet check','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_choking_hazard_sweep','Small-object and choking sweep','Choking Hazard Sweep',5,'Look under sofas, in bags, on low shelves and around older siblings'' toys. Small pieces that were once out of sight can become reachable as your toddler climbs and carries things around.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',5,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Small-object and choking sweep','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_rear_facing_car_seat','Car-seat fit and stage check','Rear Facing Car Seat',6,'Near two, the question is not just age: it is fit, weight, height, installation and history. A quick check can confirm the seat still suits your child and is being used as intended.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',6,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Car-seat fit and stage check','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_safe_sleep_continuity','Safe sleep space check-in','Safe Sleep Continuity',7,'If your toddler is climbing, wriggling or nearing a bed transition, recheck the sleep space. Keep the surface firm and flat, avoid unnecessary extras and think about the room around the bed or cot too.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',7,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Safe sleep space check-in','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_blind_cord_cleats','Blind cords and trailing wires','Blind Cord Cleats',8,'A taller toddler can reach things that used to sit above the danger line. Check blind cords, charger cables and loose wires, especially near beds, sofas and windows.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',8,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Blind cords and trailing wires','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('22-24m','22–24 months',22,24,true,'ent_cluster_22_24_reach_safety','Safety checks for a taller toddler',8,true,'ent_need_22_24_reach_safety','I can reach more now','A near-two toddler can be quick, tall and surprisingly inventive. This is a useful moment to refresh the checks that change as they climb, reach, eat more independently and travel in bigger seats: windows, cupboards, small objects, food prep, bath time, car-seat fit and sleep space.','for_you','cat_bath_supervision','Bath and water supervision','Bath Supervision',9,'Bath pouring and splashing can be brilliant at this age, but water is still a full-attention safety moment. Keep bath time supervised, prepare what you need before starting and do not leave for ‘just a second’.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',9,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,'Bath and water supervision','conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories',1,true,'ent_need_28_30_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories','Around 28-30 months, your toddler may use more two-word phrases, name things in books and ask or answer simple questions. Picture books, everyday choices and small stories give them a reason to link words together without turning talk into a test.','for_your_child','cat_picture_story_books','Picture books with questions','Picture Story Books',1,'Ask tiny who, what and where questions while you read. Naming pictures, waiting for an answer and adding one extra word can make familiar books feel fresh again at this age.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','A strong gift if the family enjoys books. Look for sturdy pages and familiar scenes.','If you already have lots of board books, choose ones with clearer stories or more to talk about.','First picture and story books','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories',1,true,'ent_need_28_30_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories','Around 28-30 months, your toddler may use more two-word phrases, name things in books and ask or answer simple questions. Picture books, everyday choices and small stories give them a reason to link words together without turning talk into a test.','for_your_child','cat_conversation_prompt_cards','Tiny question cards','Conversation Prompt Cards',2,'Simple picture or question cards can help adults remember to ask, wait and build on what the child says. Keep it playful, not quiz-like, and use them for short moments only.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',2,true,true,true,'Good gift','A thoughtful smaller gift for a chatty 2.5-year-old.','Only useful if adults will use them lightly, not as flashcards.','Toddler conversation cards','thea','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories',1,true,'ent_need_28_30_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories','Around 28-30 months, your toddler may use more two-word phrases, name things in books and ask or answer simple questions. Picture books, everyday choices and small stories give them a reason to link words together without turning talk into a test.','for_your_child','cat_songs_action_games','Action songs with choices','Songs Action Games',3,'Give familiar songs a small choice: which animal, which sound, which action comes next. It lets your toddler practise words and memory while still feeling like a game.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',3,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,NULL,'conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories',1,true,'ent_need_28_30_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories','Around 28-30 months, your toddler may use more two-word phrases, name things in books and ask or answer simple questions. Picture books, everyday choices and small stories give them a reason to link words together without turning talk into a test.','for_your_child','cat_story_replay_props','Story baskets for favourite books','Story Replay Props',4,'Put two or three safe props from a favourite book into a basket, then let your toddler retell bits their way. The story can become a little scene with words, actions and pretend play.','for_your_child','setup','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',4,false,false,false,'Setup',NULL,'Start with toys you already own before buying themed props.',NULL,'conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories',1,true,'ent_need_28_30_talk_stories_questions','I’m telling little stories','Around 28-30 months, your toddler may use more two-word phrases, name things in books and ask or answer simple questions. Picture books, everyday choices and small stories give them a reason to link words together without turning talk into a test.','for_your_child','cat_library_story_sessions','Library story sessions','Library Story Sessions',5,'A library trip gives your toddler new books, people and routines without adding clutter at home. Story sessions can also practise sitting, joining in and hearing other voices.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',5,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,NULL,'conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds',2,true,'ent_need_28_30_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds','Pretend play can shift from copying one action to running a tiny scene: teddy is tired, the train goes to the shop, or everyone gets tea. Simple props give language, memory and feelings somewhere to go.','for_your_child','cat_play_kitchen_household_props','Play kitchen and household props','Play Kitchen Household Props',1,'A pan, spoon, brush or play kitchen can turn everyday copying into a proper scene. Your toddler may stir, serve, clean and narrate what is happening, especially if you briefly join in.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','A strong gift if there is space and the family does not already have one.','If space is tight, a small tea set or pan-and-spoon basket can do the same job.','Play kitchens and household props','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds',2,true,'ent_need_28_30_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds','Pretend play can shift from copying one action to running a tiny scene: teddy is tired, the train goes to the shop, or everyone gets tea. Simple props give language, memory and feelings somewhere to go.','for_your_child','cat_doll_soft_toy_care','Soft toy and doll care play','Doll Soft Toy Care',2,'Feeding teddy, dressing a doll or tucking a soft toy into bed gives your toddler a safe way to practise care, words and routines they see every day.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',2,true,true,true,'Good gift','A lovely gift if the child enjoys caring or pushing things around.','A favourite teddy plus a blanket can work before buying a full doll set.','Dolls, soft toys and buggies','thea','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds',2,true,'ent_need_28_30_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds','Pretend play can shift from copying one action to running a tiny scene: teddy is tired, the train goes to the shop, or everyone gets tea. Simple props give language, memory and feelings somewhere to go.','for_your_child','cat_toy_cups_spoons','Tea sets, cups and little plates','Toy Cups Spoons',3,'Toy cups, spoons and plates make pretend meals easy to start. They support pouring, offering, naming and turn-taking without needing a full kitchen setup.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',3,true,true,true,'Good gift','A compact gift that supports pretend play without a big footprint.','Check pieces are large, age-fit and easy to clean.','Tea sets and picnic play','thea','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds',2,true,'ent_need_28_30_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds','Pretend play can shift from copying one action to running a tiny scene: teddy is tired, the train goes to the shop, or everyone gets tea. Simple props give language, memory and feelings somewhere to go.','for_your_child','cat_small_world_vehicles_figures','Little worlds with vehicles and figures','Small World Vehicles Figures',4,'Little people, animals, vehicles or buildings can help your toddler act out journeys, jobs and everyday scenes. At this age, the story matters more than the number of pieces.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',4,true,true,true,'Good gift','A good gift for a child who loves cars, animals or little scenes.','Avoid tiny pieces and check age labels carefully under 3.','Small-world figures and vehicles','thea','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds',2,true,'ent_need_28_30_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds','Pretend play can shift from copying one action to running a tiny scene: teddy is tired, the train goes to the shop, or everyone gets tea. Simple props give language, memory and feelings somewhere to go.','for_your_child','cat_dress_up_role_play','Dress-up and getting-ready props','Dress Up Role Play',5,'Hats, bags, loose jackets and simple props can help your toddler copy getting ready, going shopping or going to work. Keep it easy-on and low-fuss.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',5,true,true,true,'Good gift','A fun gift when clothes are loose, safe and easy to manage.','Avoid long cords, tight fastenings or anything that frustrates more than it helps.','Simple dress-up and role-play props','thea','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds',2,true,'ent_need_28_30_pretend_helper_play','I’m making pretend worlds','Pretend play can shift from copying one action to running a tiny scene: teddy is tired, the train goes to the shop, or everyone gets tea. Simple props give language, memory and feelings somewhere to go.','for_your_child','cat_play_tent_den','A little den or play tent','Play Tent Den',6,'A small den can become a shop, house, cave or quiet corner. It gives pretend play a place to happen, and can make old figures or soft toys feel interesting again.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',6,true,true,true,'Good gift','A bigger gift if the family has space and likes open-ended play.','Check space, ventilation and easy adult visibility before buying.','Play tents and small dens','thea','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_busy_hands_puzzles','My hands can solve more now',3,true,'ent_need_28_30_busy_hands_puzzles','My hands can solve more now','Small-hand play is getting more purposeful: twisting, fitting, matching, stacking, peeling and trying again. The useful challenge is not perfection, but giving hands and eyes a clear problem that can be repeated.','for_your_child','cat_shape_sorters_puzzles','Chunky puzzles and shape sorters','Shape Sorters Puzzles',1,'Chunky pieces, knobs and simple shapes let your toddler turn, test and try again. The point is not finishing neatly, but noticing what fits and changing the plan.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','A safe, classic gift when pieces are large and age-fit.','If they already have easy puzzles, look for one extra step: pegs, colour sorting or animals.','Chunky puzzles and shape sorters','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
