  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_busy_hands_puzzles','My hands can solve more now',3,true,'ent_need_28_30_busy_hands_puzzles','My hands can solve more now','Small-hand play is getting more purposeful: twisting, fitting, matching, stacking, peeling and trying again. The useful challenge is not perfection, but giving hands and eyes a clear problem that can be repeated.','for_your_child','cat_magnetic_tiles','Magnetic building tiles, age-label checked','Magnetic Tiles',4,'Magnetic tiles can grow with a child, but under-3 safety matters. Choose only age-fit sets with secure, enclosed magnets, supervise play and remove any cracked pieces immediately.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',4,true,false,false,'Parent buy',NULL,'Not all magnetic tiles are suitable under 3; check the age label and condition.','Age-fit magnetic building tiles','conor','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
