  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_feelings_turn_taking','I’m learning feelings and turn-taking',5,true,'ent_need_28_30_feelings_turn_taking','I’m learning feelings and turn-taking','Your toddler may want to be with other children but still find sharing hard. Feelings books, puppets, simple turns and gentle scripts help them practise social skills without expecting preschool-level patience.','for_your_child','cat_feelings_faces_books','Feeling stories and face books','Feelings Faces Books',1,'Books with faces, feelings and everyday upsets give toddlers language for happy, sad, cross, scared and tired. Read them when calm, not only mid-meltdown.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','A thoughtful gift for a child with big feelings or a new sibling.','Pick gentle stories rather than moral lessons.','Feelings and face books','thea','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
