  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_independence_practice','I want to do it myself',6,true,'ent_need_28_30_independence_practice','I want to do it myself','Independence can become louder at this stage. Small, safe jobs at the sink, table, coat peg or tidy-up basket let your toddler practise doing things for themselves while the adult keeps the boundaries.','for_your_child','cat_step_stool','A steady step for helping','Step Stool',1,'A stable step can let your toddler join handwashing, teeth, tidying or safe kitchen jobs. The value is independence, but the rule is adult setup and supervision.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,false,false,'Parent buy',NULL,'Supervise step use and keep away from hot, sharp or unstable surfaces.','Toddler step stools','conor','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
