  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_independence_practice','I want to do it myself',6,true,'ent_need_28_30_independence_practice','I want to do it myself','Independence can become louder at this stage. Small, safe jobs at the sink, table, coat peg or tidy-up basket let your toddler practise doing things for themselves while the adult keeps the boundaries.','for_your_child','cat_child_cleaning_helper_set','Child-size cleaning helper set','Child Cleaning Helper Set',4,'A little brush, cloth, squeegee or spray bottle with water lets your toddler copy cleaning in a contained way. It can turn ''me too'' energy into a small useful job.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',4,true,true,true,'Good gift','A fresh gift for a toddler who wants to help with everything.','Use water only and keep real cleaning products out of reach.','Child-size cleaning and helper sets','thea','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
