  ('28-30m','28–30 months',28,30,true,'ent_cluster_home_rhythm_safety','Keep bigger curiosity safer',8,true,'ent_need_28_30_home_rhythm_safety','Keep bigger curiosity safer','At 28-30 months, a toddler can reach, twist, climb and copy more than the room may expect. A short safety reset around small parts, button batteries, hot drinks, blind cords and climbable furniture is not glamorous, but it is high-value.','for_you','cat_hot_drink_bath_safety','Hot drink and bath reset','Hot Drink Bath Safety',4,'Hot drinks, bath water and garden water are ordinary parts of the day, which is why they are easy to underestimate. Keep drinks out of reach and stay with baths throughout.','for_you','safety_check','quick_checks','Quick checks',4,false,false,false,'Quick check',NULL,NULL,NULL,'conor','Save check','safety_no_shop_actions'),
