  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','Questions, stories and bigger chats',1,true,'need_language_story','I''m asking and explaining','Your child may be moving from naming things to asking why, telling little stories and explaining what happened. Books, family photos, songs and everyday chats now work best when you pause, ask and let them lead.','for_your_child','cat_why_what_chats','Why-and-what chats','Why What Chats',1,'When the ‘why?’ questions arrive, a quick answer is only half the value. Pausing, asking what they think, and adding one new word helps your child practise explaining, listening and staying in a conversation.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',1,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,NULL,'conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','Questions, stories and bigger chats',1,true,'need_language_story','I''m asking and explaining','Your child may be moving from naming things to asking why, telling little stories and explaining what happened. Books, family photos, songs and everyday chats now work best when you pause, ask and let them lead.','for_your_child','cat_picture_story_books','Picture story books with questions','Picture Story Books',2,'Books do more now when they invite your child to talk back: what is happening, what comes next, how someone feels. A familiar picture book can become a little conversation, not just a bedtime script.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',2,true,true,true,'Good gift','A strong gift if it gives grown-ups easy things to ask, not just another story.','If they already own lots of books, choose ones with richer pictures, feelings or questions.','Picture story books','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','Questions, stories and bigger chats',1,true,'need_language_story','I''m asking and explaining','Your child may be moving from naming things to asking why, telling little stories and explaining what happened. Books, family photos, songs and everyday chats now work best when you pause, ask and let them lead.','for_your_child','cat_story_sequence_cards','Story cards and sequencing games','Story Sequence Cards',3,'Putting pictures into a simple order can help your child tell a beginning, middle and end. Keep it light: silly stories, family routines and ‘what happened next?’ are enough.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',3,true,true,true,'Good gift','A thoughtful gift for a chatty nearly-three-year-old who enjoys stories.','Best if the family does not already have lots of flash-card style games.','Story and sequencing cards','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','Questions, stories and bigger chats',1,true,'need_language_story','I''m asking and explaining','Your child may be moving from naming things to asking why, telling little stories and explaining what happened. Books, family photos, songs and everyday chats now work best when you pause, ask and let them lead.','for_your_child','cat_conversation_prompt_cards','Little conversation cards','Conversation Prompt Cards',4,'A small set of prompts can rescue tired-parent chats: choose a picture, ask a silly question, remember yesterday. The value is not testing words; it is making conversation easy to start.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',4,true,true,true,'Good gift','Good for grandparents or friends who want an easy way into play.','Skip if the family dislikes card-based activities; photos work too.','Conversation prompt cards','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','Questions, stories and bigger chats',1,true,'need_language_story','I''m asking and explaining','Your child may be moving from naming things to asking why, telling little stories and explaining what happened. Books, family photos, songs and everyday chats now work best when you pause, ask and let them lead.','for_your_child','cat_songs_action_games','Songs with missing-word pauses','Songs Action Games',5,'Songs can become a talking game now. Leave out a word, pause for the action, or change the ending and let your child correct you. It supports memory, listening and turn-taking without needing a new toy.','for_your_child','activity','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',5,false,false,false,'Idea',NULL,NULL,NULL,'conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_talk_stories_questions','Questions, stories and bigger chats',1,true,'need_language_story','I''m asking and explaining','Your child may be moving from naming things to asking why, telling little stories and explaining what happened. Books, family photos, songs and everyday chats now work best when you pause, ask and let them lead.','for_your_child','cat_family_photo_story_cards','Family photo story cards','Family Photo Story Cards',6,'Print a few family photos or use a small album: who was there, what happened first, what happened next? Real people and real places can make storytelling easier than abstract cards.','for_your_child','setup','useful_ideas','Useful ideas',6,false,false,false,'Setup',NULL,NULL,NULL,'conor','Save idea','no_shop_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_social_worlds','Pretend play with people, places and feelings',2,true,'need_pretend_worlds','I''m making whole little worlds','Pretend play can stretch from copying one action to building a whole scenario: the car goes camping, the doll needs bed, the shop opens, someone feels sad. Props help when they leave room for your child’s idea.','for_your_child','cat_small_world_figures','Small-world people and vehicles','Small World Figures',1,'Little figures, animals and vehicles can support whole scenes now: someone gets in, goes somewhere, needs help, comes home. Choose simple, sturdy pieces that leave space for your child’s story.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',1,true,true,true,'Good gift','Good if it adds people, vehicles or animals to play they already enjoy.','If they already have figures, add a missing theme rather than a bigger set.','Small-world people and vehicles','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_social_worlds','Pretend play with people, places and feelings',2,true,'need_pretend_worlds','I''m making whole little worlds','Pretend play can stretch from copying one action to building a whole scenario: the car goes camping, the doll needs bed, the shop opens, someone feels sad. Props help when they leave room for your child’s idea.','for_your_child','cat_modular_playhouse','Simple playhouse or scene set','Modular Playhouse',2,'A small house, shop, garage or campsite gives your child a stage for stories. The best version is not busy; it lets them move people around and decide what is happening.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',2,true,true,true,'Good gift','A higher-value gift when several relatives want one lasting present.','Check whether the family already has a play kitchen, dolls’ house or garage.','Simple playhouse or scene set','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_social_worlds','Pretend play with people, places and feelings',2,true,'need_pretend_worlds','I''m making whole little worlds','Pretend play can stretch from copying one action to building a whole scenario: the car goes camping, the doll needs bed, the shop opens, someone feels sad. Props help when they leave room for your child’s idea.','for_your_child','cat_doll_soft_toy_care','Dolls and soft-toy care play','Doll Soft Toy Care',3,'Feeding, tucking in, helping and comforting a doll or teddy can make everyday care visible. It is useful because the story includes language, emotion and gentle sequencing.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',3,true,true,true,'Good gift','Good if the child enjoys copying family routines or caring for teddies.','A doll they already love may be enough; accessories can refresh the play.','Dolls and soft-toy care play','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_social_worlds','Pretend play with people, places and feelings',2,true,'need_pretend_worlds','I''m making whole little worlds','Pretend play can stretch from copying one action to building a whole scenario: the car goes camping, the doll needs bed, the shop opens, someone feels sad. Props help when they leave room for your child’s idea.','for_your_child','cat_play_kitchen_household_props','Pretend food and café play','Play Kitchen Household Props',4,'A café, picnic or kitchen game lets your child copy jobs they see all day: stirring, serving, choosing, paying, tidying. It works best when you join the story rather than direct it.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',4,true,true,true,'Good gift','Good if it adds a fresh role to a kitchen or picnic setup.','High ownership risk: many families already have kitchen or food props.','Pretend food and café play','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
  ('34-36m','34–36 months',34,36,true,'ent_cluster_pretend_social_worlds','Pretend play with people, places and feelings',2,true,'need_pretend_worlds','I''m making whole little worlds','Pretend play can stretch from copying one action to building a whole scenario: the car goes camping, the doll needs bed, the shop opens, someone feels sad. Props help when they leave room for your child’s idea.','for_your_child','cat_dress_up_role_play','Dress-up and role-play basket','Dress Up Role Play',5,'A hat, bag, scarf or safe costume piece can help a child step into a role. Keep it simple and safe: avoid long loose cords, and choose pieces that can be used in lots of stories.','for_your_child','product_category','things_that_can_help','Things that can help',5,true,true,true,'Good gift','Good when it is open-ended, not a single-use costume.','A few everyday accessories can work as well as a costume set.','Dress-up and role-play basket','both','See Ember Picks','product_actions'),
